          "reviewBody": "Learning can be so majestic....yes recently we visited the science exhibition organised by one of the prestigious school of Gurgaon, Shalom Presidency School.\nEverything seemed to be so perfect and flawless....\n\nThe school works on the overall development and grooming of a student.\nThe compassion, commitment and dedication of the of the Founder of the school, Dr Lilly George, also known as MD Ma'am, is outstanding and sets an example for her teachers and her students.\nA highly recommended school with world class amenities, the indoor swimming pool, a home away from home day care, the labs are well equipped.\nWorld class education under one roof.",
