            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My child has been attending Shalom Presidency School for the past six years, and I am happy with the education and experience he has received. The teachers are knowledgeable, compassionate, and go above and beyond to ensure that each child is receiving personalized attention and support. The school's emphasis on character development and community involvement has helped my child develop important social and emotional skills that will benefit them for a lifetime. I highly recommend Shalom Presidency School to any parent looking for an excellent education for their child.",
